Section 3. Information about an individual who is a party to a controlled transaction (group of similar transactions)
1. Sequence number of the controlled transaction (from Section 1A)
2. Порядковый номер участника контролируемой сделки (из Раздела 1Б)
2. Sequence number of the controlled transaction party (from Section 1B)
3. Data is filled with respect to consignee (commission agent)
Middle name is specified if any.
Подраздел заполняется в отношении физических лиц - резидентов Российской Федерации, не имеющих ИНН, и физических лиц - нерезидентов
The subsection is filled in for individuals who are the residents of the Russian Federation and do not have the TIN, and individuals who are non-residents
